io.github.trulyfree.easyaspi.lib.callback

Interface StagedCallback

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Callback
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmptyCallback

    public interface StagedCallback
extends Callback
    A Callback interface extension which defines the setStages method. This allows sections of progress to be defined. Note that onStart, onProgress and onFinish methods should be called on the start, progress, and finish of each stage, respectively.
    Since:
    v0.0.1-alpha
    Author:
    vtcakavsmoace
